org.apache.chemistry.opencmis.client.api

Interface ObjectFactory


  • public interface ObjectFactory
    A factory to create and convert CMIS objects. Custom ObjectFactory implementations may use the convert methods to inject specific implementations of the interfaces when the data is transfered from the low level API to the high level API.
    See Also:
    Session.getObjectFactory()

      • createContentStream

        ContentStream createContentStream(String filename,
                                long length,
                                String mimetype,
                                InputStream stream)
        Creates an object that implements the ContentStream interface.
        Parameters:
        filename - the filename, should be set
        length - the length of the stream or -1 if the length is unknown
        mimetype - the MIME type, if unknown "application/octet-stream" should be used
        stream - the stream, should not be null
        Returns:
        the ContentStream object

      • createContentStream

        ContentStream createContentStream(String filename,
                                long length,
                                String mimetype,
                                InputStream stream,
                                boolean partial)
        Creates an object that implements the ContentStream interface.
        Parameters:
        filename - the filename, should be set
        length - the length of the stream or -1 if the length is unknown
        mimetype - the MIME type, if unknown "application/octet-stream" should be used
        stream - the stream, should not be null
        partial - if false the stream represents the full content, if true the stream is only a part of the content
        Returns:
        the ContentStream object
